    Bot must have customizible Categories.
    Every Category has it's over budged.
    User can add categories, set up budged, add transactions and see statistics,
including how much money does it have.

Chat example:
    /add Transfer
    Transfer category have been added.
    /budged Transfer 30
    Transfer now have budged of 30
    /spend Transfer 30
    /revent
    Last transaction is deleted